document.full_text: libya's rebel army has replaced ragtag volunteers with polished officers to guard the flash-point eastern town of ajdabiyah, as it seeks to bolster its image as a credible adversary of muammar gaddafi.
document.title: libya rebels try to impose order, boost credibility
